    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear or creasing, and the original protective films remain on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at the authorized dealership on a strictly time-based schedule, regardless of the exceptionally low mileage. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. The sale includes all original keys, the window sticker, a complete set of owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive binder of service records. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a turn-key vehicle that presents as if it just left the assembly line.",
      "price": 44900.0,
